  "texts": [
    "For the Chinese model, the removed layers are [7, 25, 3, 4, 29, 15, 26, 20, 24, 5, 10, 9, 27, 28, 18, 13].",
    "The layers are listed from most to least important (left to right), according to the layer importance evaluation used in our iterative pruning method.",
    "In this experiment, all 32 encoder layers are kept intact; therefore, the table reports the remaining decoder layers as 24/32, 22/32, 20/32, and 16/32 encoder/decoder layers.",
    "fine-tuning is performed 8 times, once after each pruning step.",
    "By the end of the process, the pruned layers for German are [13, 1, 3, 17, 12, 4, 14, 21], based on layer importance evaluation."
  ]
